\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x\in B\implies f(x)=p\circ j(x)=p(x)=x+I
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\align left
Es decir, 
\begin_inset Formula $Imf=\frac{B}{I}$
\end_inset

